  ## Delete Credit Note Reason
  ลบเหตุผลใบลดหนี้ตาม ID

  Soft-deletes a credit note reason. Historical records using this reason are preserved.

  ### Path Parameters
  - `id` -- Credit note reason ID (UUID) / รหัสเหตุผลใบลดหนี้


  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "uuid"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```
}

